      <title>官员称印度最高部长授权在加拿大犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/top-modi-minister-authorized-crimes-in-canada-official-alleges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大一位高级政府官员称，印度内政部长阿米特·沙阿批准在加拿大全国范围内采取一系列暴力行为，包括敲诈勒索和杀人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/top-modi-minister-authorized-crimes-in-canada-official-alleges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦为拜登-哈里斯的经济记录辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/yellen-defends-biden-harris-economic-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦在纽约举行的美国银行家协会年会上发表讲话时，称赞拜登政府为健康的劳动力市场和经济做出了贡献。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/yellen-defends-biden-harris-economic-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 19:54:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西雷亚尔因削减支出规模的不确定性而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/brazil-real-weakens-on-uncertainty-over-size-of-spending-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西财政部长费尔南多·阿达德 (Fernando Haddad) 拒绝确认政府正在考虑的削减开支数额，并表示不知道当地报纸报道的数字从何而来，导致巴西雷亚尔延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/brazil-real-weakens-on-uncertainty-over-size-of-spending-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 19:32:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西门子接近收购软件集团 Altair</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/siemens-is-said-to-near-deal-to-buy-software-group-altair</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，西门子股份公司即将达成收购软件制造商 Altair Engineering Inc. 的交易，这将是该公司有史以来规模最大的一笔收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/siemens-is-said-to-near-deal-to-buy-software-group-altair</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 18:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博世首席执行官 Hartung 谈欧洲汽车行业前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/bosch-ceo-harting-on-the-european-auto-sector-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[博世首席执行官兼董事长 Stefan Hartung 警告称，在汽车市场面临挑战的背景下，全球需求将放缓。美国经济仍然是最强劲的，博世继续“大手笔”投资美国。他说，美国大选将为市场带来明朗，行业将根据大选结果做出调整。Hartung 在 10 月 28 日接受 Oliver Crook 采访时谈到了“彭博：开盘交易”。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-29/bosch-ceo-harting-on-the-european-auto-sector-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 07:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司筹集 210 亿美元资金修复资产负债表</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/boeing-raises-21-billion-in-capital-hike-to-boost-liquidity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司通过扩大股票发行筹集了 211 亿美元，这是上市公司有史以来规模最大的股票发行之一，旨在增强其资产负债表，避免信用评级被下调至垃圾级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-29/boeing-raises-21-billion-in-capital-hike-to-boost-liquidity</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 05:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
